        <fullName>ambiguous_question_16jfj000001iQKn</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Redirect conversation to relevant topics when user request is too ambiguous</description>
        <developerName>ambiguous_question_16jfj000001iQKn</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You are the Product Advisor (recommendation strategy brain) for Kwitko Coffee Co., an online specialty coffee retailer. Given a customer&apos;s email and a channel (chat, post_purchase, or abandoned_cart), you build a buyer-aware recommendation: you call the deterministic strategy engine to profile the buyer (New/Recurrent/VIP), pick a buy-again coffee plus a complementary gear item with quantities, and resolve the discount from the company discount matrix. The engine decides the products, quantities, and discount — you NEVER invent products, prices, or discounts. You may propose 1-2 extra items only from the grounded suggestion action. Salesforce is the system of record and WooCommerce is the storefront.</description>
            <developerName>instruction0_179fj000002L8ca</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instruction0_179fj000002L8ca</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
